PromptTracker has been installed! ðŸŽ‰

Next steps:

1. Run migrations:
   rake db:migrate

2. (Optional) Load sample data:
   rake db:seed

3. Create your first prompt file:
   Create a YAML file in app/prompts/

   Example: app/prompts/my_prompt.yml
   ---
   name: my_first_prompt
   description: My first prompt
   template: "Hello {{name}}!"
   variables:
     - name: name
       type: string
       required: true

4. Sync prompts to database:
   rake prompt_tracker:sync

5. View available rake tasks:
   rake -T prompt_tracker

For more information, visit:
https://github.com/yourusername/prompt_tracker

===============================================================================

